data.title: Los Angeles Murders and Homicides
data.meta_description: Los Angeles County murder and homicides victims, and their stories.
data.text:

Gilbert Rodriguez, a 55-year-old Latino male, died Monday, Dec. 25, at 1662 East Florence Avenue, according to Los Angeles County Medical Examiner-Coroner's records.
